txt.en: The stone-giant Helf has stolen the egg of a Great Eagle. The egg must be protected from Helf's devious ambitions and returned, undamaged, to the Great Eagles.
Complete the quest: Iorbar's Peak -- Challenge
You must protect the egg from Helf's devious ambitions and return it, undamaged, to the possession of the Eagles.
